tool-base 2.0.0-SNAPSHOT.28 API

Packages 
Package Description
io.spine.tools
This package provides types for working with programming tools.
io.spine.tools.archive
This package contains classes working with archive files.
io.spine.tools.code
This package contains tools for generating and working with source code.
io.spine.tools.dart.fs
This package contains tools for working with the structure of a Dart project.
io.spine.tools.fs
This package contains tools for working with the structure of a project.
io.spine.tools.java.code
This package contains tools for generating Java code as well as working with already generated code.
io.spine.tools.java.code.column
This package contains the routines for generating strongly-typed columns for the entity state messages.
io.spine.tools.java.code.field
This package contains the routines for generating strongly-typed fields for the subscribable message types.
io.spine.tools.java.code.query
This package contains the routines performing the assembly of Query and QueryBuilder code generated for entity state types.
io.spine.tools.java.fs
This package contains tools for working with the structure of a Java project.
io.spine.tools.java.javadoc
Utilities for working with Javadoc.
io.spine.tools.js.code
This package contains tools for generating Java code as well as working with already generated code.
io.spine.tools.js.fs
This package contains tools for working with the structure of a JavaScript project.
io.spine.tools.proto.fs
This package contains types for working file system aspects of Protobuf definitions.
io.spine.tools.protoc
This package provides extension points for Protoc plugins.
io.spine.tools.type
This package contains utilities for the Spine type system for the needs of the compile-time checkers and processors.
